title: Grateful Dead Live at Unknown on 1980-01-01
description:
Set I
Side A

Pigpen
Phil Lesh
Tom Constanten
Paul Foster
Mike Ferguson
Gary Duncan
Set II
Side B

Jerry Garcia
Pigpen


Comment
Hank Harrison - 'Dead Archives'

Interviews from the 1960s and 1970s, assembled and introduced by Hank Harrison in 1980 (who makes reference to it as being a C60 cassette).
